des:
Alexa will tell you which exercise to do and then the timer will start. She'll then let you know when to take a break. 

Other features:
- 50+ exercises (to develop every muscle)
- Unique workouts every time (variety is the spice of life)
- Adjustable intensity (suitable for everyone)
- Choose how long you want to workout (fit it in to your schedule)
- Timed breaks (rest is important)
- NEW Rep counter (Smash your goals)
- NEW reminders (Create a habit)
